## table card | under=proj_default | doc="Status value-cards. is_terminal flags Done/Cancelled so the predicate compiler can hide tasks pointing at them via notTerminal(status)."
### rows
card_type_id,     parent_card_id, is_terminal, title,       sort_order, alias
$card_type.status, parent,         false,       "Todo",      1,         s_todo
$card_type.status, parent,         false,       "Doing",     2,         s_doing
$card_type.status, parent,         false,       "Review",    3,         s_review
$card_type.status, parent,         true,        "Done",      4,         s_done
$card_type.status, parent,         true,        "Cancelled", 5,         s_cancel


